{"tid":1890673,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"有郵輪旅客認為日本政府對香港人不公平 日後或者不會再到日本","createTime":"2020-02-21T10:10:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-21T10:37:28.000Z","uid":117837,"like":7,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"58a86a0d2f9e73e20f643e8e0b21e6a522f56cdf","tid":1890673,"uid":117837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T10:10:31.000Z","msg":"政府為滯留在日本橫濱「鑽石公主號」郵輪港人的第二班包機，最快日本時間傍晚6時起飛。乘坐這班機的第二批港人，陸續抵羽田機場辦理手續。<br />\n<br />\n在日本時間3時許，接載他們的旅遊巴先後抵達羽田機場，這批港人都戴上口罩，部分人更戴上手套，全部頸上掛有粉紅色牌，以識別身份。穿上防護衣物的入境處人員，在機場設置特別櫃位協助他們。<br />\n<br />\n剛今日生日的黃先生說，今次經歷很難受，過了一個難忘的生日，希望能快點回家。他說每日在船上聽到幾十又幾十人染病，感到驚恐，擔心會染病；感覺到命運已不是掌握在自己手中，處境危險，不是小心便能避免要講運氣。<br />\n<br />\n和朋友一行8人參加郵輪旅遊的<span style=\"color: red;\">植女士</span>，對於船公司安排滿意度一半半，<span style=\"color: red;\">認為日本政府對香港人不公平，不應該這樣對<strong>中國人</strong></span>，第二班包機明明安排於昨晚啟程，但卻讓其他國家的乘客先走。她說香港政府已盡力，但不夠強及欠缺「牙力」，<span style=\"color: red;\">她日後或者不會再到日本。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1509953-20200221.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1509953-20200221.htm&d=8qD7g5vOfNqkLkogRxTPVCPhHSzXeBMEaaQhzK3ZYsY%3D&h=10870565\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1509953-20200221.htm&h=6bfb14de\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1509953-20200221.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n開錯台 再開過"},{"pid":"24ecd1e85cda6a39efe507c580be7da8aab76ef3","tid":1890673,"uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T10:12:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41a1db4c0a723279ae215337b7b7ed94a7f944df","tid":1890673,"uid":67340,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T10:12:23.000Z","msg":"中國人=病源<br />\n明明係災害仲要人唔差別對待你？香港冇你呢啲垃圾人"},{"pid":"6b81cf27c0243fce10b4d636336366304fafb8a7","tid":1890673,"uid":254183,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T10:12:52.000Z","msg":"支那賤畜<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02b49239347029ec6617e7797ae2a3c59ec59c61","tid":1890673,"uid":249885,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T10:13:09.000Z","msg":"日本狗殺害香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da05aa18981e169d10d9c5c59ac14348b1ce1a7c","tid":1890673,"uid":3020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T10:13:46.000Z","msg":"佢地對香港人都不公平<br />\n<br />\n可否要求佢地不可離港"},{"pid":"5e31f4a90955016936e98c30db7b488e78e82936","tid":1890673,"uid":38761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T10:13:47.000Z","msg":"希望講得出，做得定啦！"},{"pid":"884914052b655a16cb460ea436f0cd6f8b01ec3f","tid":1890673,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T10:13:49.000Z","msg":"支持你啊 支那狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18128a11b7f69f87902e775f91cb14d891ee5ad5","tid":1890673,"uid":48458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"58a86a0d2f9e73e20f643e8e0b21e6a522f56cdf","tid":1890673,"uid":117837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T10:10:31.000Z","msg":"政府為滯留在日本橫濱「鑽石公主號」郵輪港人的第二班包機，最快日本時間傍晚6時起飛。乘坐這班機的第二批港人，陸續抵羽田機場辦理手續。<br />\n<br />\n在日本時間3時許，接載他們的旅遊巴先後抵達羽田機